lead_paragraph: Thorbjorn Olesen extended his lead to seven strokes at the Turkish Airlines Open after shooting 3-under 68 for his third round on Saturday, moving the Dane to the brink of a European Tour victory for the third straight year.

headline.print_headline: Olesen Shoots 68, Leads by 7 at Turkish Airlines Open
